[DhtmlXQ_comment160]！||如附图所示，黑方兑车妙手，获胜关键之着。[/DhtmlXQ_comment160]
[DhtmlXQ_comment162]！||献马妙用“引离”战术，精彩入局。[/DhtmlXQ_comment162]
[DhtmlXQ_comment166]捉死红马，黑胜。[/DhtmlXQ_comment166]
